2022 was an amazing year for me! 
•
I got to skate the top hill on my bucket list, made lots of new friends, got too drunk at every skate event, surprised myself with my skating, and got a pro model (which will definitely make you skate like me if you ride one😉) Code JAKE10 for 10% off at rayne.com📈
•
Big thanks to everyone who made this year one to remember ❤️
